I'll just leave this here. Throw this into your browser's Javascript Console:Code:var autoCookieClick = setInterval(Game.ClickCookie, 1);That takes care of that pesky cookie clicking, and you can focus on buying things and clicking golden cookies.To stop:Code:clearInterval(autoCookieClick);
